    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Large result sets (up to 100.000 hits) request is too slow. It should be optimized.</p>

<p>The ferst idea is:
Score is usually (for Term and MultiTerm queries) calculated based on term freq, but Zend_Search_Lucene requests full list of terms positions. It can be omitted.</p>

<p>There are also some other places, which can be optimized.</p>

